      <title>BMO的Kaushik对关税对加拿大经济的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-05/bmo-s-kaushik-on-impact-of-tariffs-to-canadian-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫周三表示，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在墨西哥和加拿大新强加的关税中免于对汽车制造商的新征收关税。 BMO的高级经济学家兼副总裁经济学Shelly Kaushik在“彭博市场”上解释了（消息来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-05/bmo-s-kaushik-on-impact-of-tariffs-to-canadian-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 19:05:34 GMT</pubDate>
